metadata.name: HuangFei #1
metadata.description: The Imperial Palace has 4444 Huangfei NFT, the beauties all over Han Dynasty. The Huangfei is an NFT collection minted on the Ethereum blockchain, bridging the gap between the past, Web3, and the real world. We are set in the Han Dynasty, the most prosperous period in Chinese history. Will your Huangfei NFT be the Hwanghu or will you be her own Emperor?
